§I CLASSIFICATION-LEGEND
  ⟦
    ✓ DISCIPLINED   · spec has mechanically-verifiable acceptance criteria in some form
    ◐ PARTIAL       · spec has rules / criteria but mechanical verification incomplete
    ◯ PROCESS       · spec is vision / progress / strategy / audit · lighter requirements appropriate
    ‼ HIGH-RISK    · feature/architecture spec without any clear acceptance criteria · retro-amend candidate
    📄 SAMPLED      · this auditor deep-read the spec · classification confirmed
    📋 INFERRED     · classification by filename + repo-context · not deep-read · subject to confirmation
  ⟧

