        priority-4 : remaining PARTIAL specs as time-allows
      effort : ~1-2 agent-hours per spec · ~15 specs · ~20-30 agent-hours total
      gate   : per-spec amendment-trailer · ratified · committed
      cadence : 2-3 specs per session · spread over ~5 sessions

